Comment: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ending Keyframe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.31,0:00:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fumizuki Academy is a new school that has\Nimplemented a special system for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.38,0:00:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, please begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first part of this system is the Exam Summoning Battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battles are waged between\NSummoned Beings of different classes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.62,0:00:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which are given form by the latest technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other key element of the system is classroom\Nfacilities which directly correspond to one's ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Students take a placement exam at the end of each school year,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and are then divided into six classes\Nfrom A through F based on their scores.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally time to take the placement exam...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.14,0:00:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't gonna be a walk in the park, but I can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himeji!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving the room during the exam will result in a zero. Am I clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.34,0:01:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But teach!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Yoshii?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.93,0:01:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.04,0:01:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ironman...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Mr. Nishimura, not Ironman.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.58,0:01:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go. You're the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.79,0:01:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the results of your placement exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be assigned to whatever class is written in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.27,0:01:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I might as well tell you this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.80,0:01:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After everything you showed me last year, I had my suspicions that you were an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.91,0:01:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, after I saw your score, I realized that I was mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.77,0:02:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to apologize for doubting you, Yoshii. You're not an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one hell of an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Fumizuki Academy is a new school that has\Nimplemented a special system for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? Class F?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the worst class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought I was gonna do well, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I have to have at least gotten 10% right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fumizuki Academy is a new school that takes pride in the fact that it uses only the latest study materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,System desks and reclining seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They even have laptops!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.02,0:04:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear lord, a self-serving bar! Class A\Ncan have snacks whenever they want!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw floors... Floor cushions... Coffee tables...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my classroom!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reality is a harsh mistress at Fumizuki Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If one wishes to have a more comfortable educational experience, he or she must make better grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the academy's central tenet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God damn... So I guess this is a caste system, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii, hurry up and sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Where do I sit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.81,0:05:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no seating chart!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, my cushion doesn't have any stuffing in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but there's wind blowing in from the crack in the window. It's quite chilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, my table broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, reality is truly cruel at Fumizuki Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Fukuhara, the teacher for this class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we'll have a-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go get this fixed. You\Ncan study whatever in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this place sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to spend the entire year here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, man, you shoulda scored better on the test if you were gonna bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuji! You're in this class too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look who else is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! Looks like I'm stuck here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimada!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm not surprised you're in F.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you calling me an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owowowowow! This shit hurts when chicks without any tits do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nearly there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't lived in Japan for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I couldn't read the questions, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's pretty lively in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideyoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in this class too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.08,0:06:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopefully this won't suck too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can drink to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, yeah, this is the worst class in the entire school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the guys in here look retarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That includes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.74,0:06:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness we have a cute girl like Hideyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls are beings who are so gentle and\Nkind that they can mend a broken heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:06:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimada, on the other hand,\Nis rough, frightening, and flat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus Christ, my spine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, I'm sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himeji...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna snap my spine into two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna break... You bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:35.73,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Nearly there...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave us, Voyeur!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Li... Li...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk! I'll call an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Voyeur!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at least I'm not the only girl here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:08:00.52,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Voyeur! I'll save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:03.71,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Save him! Somebody save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:08:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no seating chart, so sit wherever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, is that seat free?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.39,0:08:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you got placed into class F...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's make the best of it-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is worn out as hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, the cushions might as well be rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The floor's a veritable breeding ground for mold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't somewhere a sick person should be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't school, like, a microcosm of society?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare they segregate us like this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they'll treat us like dogs if we complain about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:08:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As such, we'll simply have to challenge them fair and square.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we come into power and gain the right to speak up, we'll tell the world about-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you want somewhere more amenable to Himeji, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on! I was trying to make it sound all noble!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.22,0:09:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you have to ruin it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I was thinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to prove to the world that grades aren't everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty confident, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.73,0:09:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna try it, Akihisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's try out an Exam Summoning Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to propose something as your class representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want us to engage in an Exam Summoning Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Exam Summoning Battle? What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fumizuki Academy has a system called the Exam Summoning Battle, also known as the ESB.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under the supervision of a teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,students can summon a Being with attack power proportional to their grades in a given subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can challenge other classes using these Beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:10:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a lower level class defeats a higher level\None, they will swap facilities and classrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, are you happy with this crappy room?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we win an ESB,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be able to get class A's fabulous room!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the lowest class.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bottom of this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're nothing but a bunch of garbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that means that we have nothing to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why don't we give it a shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we have him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii Akihisa is a legendary Punishment Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! I've never seen one before!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! He's left me in despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Himeji?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are Punishment Inspectors strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.49,0:10:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Only very special people can be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a title given to mentally\Ndisabled kids who get bad grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It translates to "Idiot".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, a worthless piece of crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just take me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we win an ESB, we can kiss this classroom goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What say we give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to start with the class directly above us - class E.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa, you're now class F's ambassador.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go and declare war on class E.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bad things happen to ambassadors from weaker countries when they declare war?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, only in movies and novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, who on Earth would mess with an ambassador?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa, you're the only one who can do this for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretend that I tricked you or something. Hop to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tricked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this is about what I thought would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You predicted this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duh. I'm the rep for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least act like you're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can no longer turn back, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:11:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this what you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Don't worry, I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? The sophomores have declared an ESB during the first semester?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have my permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put on a nice show for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our supervisor is Mr. Hasegawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seize him right before fifth period, while he's walking to class E.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hasegawa, the math teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Math is my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Shimada will be our\Nmainline, since she's good at math.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himeji, are you good at math?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then team up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.94,0:12:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.07,0:12:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your attack points are equal to the\Ngrade you received on your last test.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our last test was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The placement exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:13:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to leave during the exam, so I got a 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can take a recovery exam once the ESB begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Himeji takes it, she'll be able to join us when she finishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.07,0:13:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've seized Mr. Hasegawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for war, people! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For crying out loud... these guys are friggin' morons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.23,0:13:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, it's time to sortie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go teach those failures a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.72,0:13:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minami Shimada, reporting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:13:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideyoshi Kinoshita, ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kouta Tsychiya, same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Permitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summoning Being!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was I the only one with a transformation sequence?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful. Living flesh can't cross that barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna get past here, you're gonna have to beat us first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshiko Mika, I accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way class E can beat me at math!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who were KIA, meet in the detention room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ironman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Acording to ESB rules, those whose points reach zero must receive supplementary lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.71,0:15:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me! I don't want to have detention with this monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to pass, then you have to defeat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's our plan, Yuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like tug-of-war - whichever class gets\Npushed back will have their classroom invaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.83,0:15:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if their rep gets defeated, that side loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.50,0:15:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't happen to us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:16:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! They're pushing us back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.07,0:16:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class E has better grades overall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we go head to head, it's only a matter of time before we lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, they are only class E. It'll take them a while to make it all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the time it'll take them to do that is the key to our victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My points...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna murder us at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on standby and recover your points.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to take the recovery test!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you recieve on this test will become your Being's attack points the next time you summon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.26,0:16:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you score low, then your Being will become weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which subject?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Math, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to answer as much as I can to recover my points...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:16:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Voyeur!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.46,0:17:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.81,0:17:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assault them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.61,0:17:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our defensive line is down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad, Yuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.93,0:17:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Numbers are just numbers... they're not Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh god, kanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.91,0:17:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll skip this question.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who were KIA, meet in the detention room!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Yuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:18:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but it looks like it's about time for us to end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, coming here yourself, eh? Don't underestimate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys idiots? You declared an ESB as soon as school began.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just finished taking the placement exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.76,0:18:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our differences in class are equivalent to our differences in points.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really think you'd win?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are in class F because you're so stupid, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuji, we're not going to be able to beat the classes above us without a plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I do have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Know why I kept you with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct! He's Akihisa Yoshii, the Punishment Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa, show them your true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I've got no choice... It always comes down to me in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Punishment Inspector's Being has special powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.58,0:19:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it has to assist teachers with their chores as punishment,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.84,0:19:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's corporeal, unlike the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, any pain it feels will be felt by its summoner as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.93,0:19:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of that small fry first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.39,0:19:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't take me down that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owowowowowow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes sense that you're the rep for E class.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your bodyguard's pretty damn useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, he's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish you off personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Hiromi Nakabayashi, challenge you, Yuuji Sakamoto, to-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:20:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki Himeji, I accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summoning Being.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are her points so high!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is class A level!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is a student like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himeji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.55,0:20:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki Himeji... Don't tell me... you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinada?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's totally awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder she was a candidate for class A...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Himeji's score?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Fumizuki Academy, you can take as many tests as you wish during the testing period.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As such, you can acquire as points as you are capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.65,0:20:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, your plan was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to buy time while she took the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one told me she was in class F!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.68,0:20:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Exam Summoning Battle ends in class F's victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're amazing, Himeji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're just saying that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we can switch classrooms and facilities with class E!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's better, at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we're not switching facilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll keep what we have now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you think it's a good idea, Nakabayashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.39,0:21:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Yuuji? I mean, we won!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's over?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideyoshi, why are you dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, that's it. You've finally understood the calling in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm over here, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.05,0:21:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.69,0:21:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.36,0:21:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideyoshi is my twin brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the ambassador from class 2A, Yuuko Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:22:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, class A, declare war on you, class F.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is class A declaring war on us!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think we'll go easy on you just because you're the lowest class.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.45,0:22:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to obliterate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Question 2:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.85,0:23:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please answer the following question:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.03,0:23:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This plant has roots which can be eaten. In English, it is known as a "lily".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.89,0:23:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yam! Potato! Sweet potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.28,0:23:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please also pay attention to the second part of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:23:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Lilies and Roses and PE.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.78,0:23:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be on your test.
