Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:24.02,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HF1DEEB&}Just who are we letting grow up on their own?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.56,0:02:42.20,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HFFF3BA&}Meeting someone else is the easy way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:44.86,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HEBD5FE&}I knew what I would say before they even asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:47.40,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HB1FFB2&}Do I look lovestruck enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:49.63,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HC9E4FF&}I'm not gonna lose my cool, love's at stake!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:52.66,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HCAC7FF&}Study! Study! Study! It keeps me up all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:55.30,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HFFC9EB&}I've got a genius inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.46,0:02:57.88,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HA0E6FF&}It'd be great if my dreams came true
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:03:00.13,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HD6C3CB&}because I don't care about anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:02.74,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HD5CDFF&}Perfect area complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:05.44,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HCDFFDC&}I'll be waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:12.02,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HFFFED3&}I can hear your voice from the perfect area ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:15.33,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HE8D4FF&}Fly! I won't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:19.25,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HBBECFF&}Yeah, that's me, the person you just passed by.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:20.55,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HFFCABF&}Are we still friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:23.73,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HABFFC7&}I flunked our friendship test, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:27.05,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&H889DF8&}No! I'll take it again! Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:29.16,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HFFD8BF&}Come on, gimme another chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:33.48,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HFFEBBF&}Something better awaits us in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:39.99,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HD7C3FD&}A better life awaits us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:25.05,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\an8\c&H9BBAFF&}One more chance! One more chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.14,0:02:26.37,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\an8\c&H9BBAFF&}Never, never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.44,0:02:27.70,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\an8\c&HFFC7C4&}One more chance! One more chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:28.65,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\an8\c&HFFC7C4&}Never give up!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.72,0:22:31.67,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&HC45007&}It's a time of peace now that school's out.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.77,0:22:34.70,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&HC45007&}If I were to describe her, she's a real angel!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.86,0:22:37.70,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H9100FE&}Then came a notice that shattered my fun.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.84,0:22:40.48,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H9100FE&}It said I had to stay afterschool! It's like hell!!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.89,0:22:43.75,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H0FF606&}I was talking about it with my friends, and I said,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.90,0:22:46.75,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H0FF606&}"No way anyone's that stupid!!"
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.95,0:22:49.87,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H0000BC&}But deep inside me,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.00,0:22:52.37,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H0000BC&}I was shouting out,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.58,0:22:54.12,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H0000BC&}"I AM THAT STUPID!"
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.68,0:22:57.25,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&H3300AE&\c&H000000&}That sign in the parking lot
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.71,0:23:00.46,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&H3300AE&\c&H000000&}that says "Monthly"...{or "Tsukigime"}
Dialogue: 1,0:23:00.82,0:23:05.95,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&H3300AE&\c&H000000&}I always thought that was the company's name.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.14,0:23:08.60,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ALWAYS.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.58,0:23:12.31,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&HA23500&}Stupidity's a character! A real man!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.59,0:23:15.24,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&HA23500&}Our common sense is the lack thereof!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.63,0:23:18.28,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H1F009B&}We don't need rules in our fucking world!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:18.64,0:23:21.33,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H1F009B&}Eat steak out every night, overthrow the mass!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:21.73,0:23:27.75,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H99A000&}Take a look, the sun that rose from the west is setting back down!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:27.75,0:23:30.81,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H99A000&}Run home, it's almost dinner!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:30.81,0:23:33.47,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H99A000&}Let's get home!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:33.84,0:23:37.53,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H99A000&}Let's get home!
